海底捞回应顾客确诊新冠肺炎：涉事门店已全面消毒，员工目前身体状况正常。
Bottom fishing in response to customers confirmed the new crown pneumonia: the shop has been fully disinfected, the staff is now in normal health.
张钦。
Zhang Chin.
