界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
图片来源：图虫记者：张钦  编辑：昝慧昉“ 此前海底捞发布公告称，考虑到近期疫情发展情况，中国内地门店停业时间将会继续延长。
(Source: Toothworm) Zhang Hui-fang (pictured here) "The shutdown of shops in mainland China will continue to be extended due to the recent development of the epidemic," said Zhang Huifang, editor of Zhangqin.
”近日，江苏省常州市发布《关于紧急扩散寻找相关接触者的通知》：常州市在排查确诊的新型冠状病毒感染的病例时，发现第27例确诊病例（男性）曾于1月22日18:47—20:43与多位朋友在海底捞火锅店（新北区丰臣国际）就餐，桌号为93号，同桌就餐的共有5人（男性4人，女性1人），其中2人已被确诊为新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎病例，3人已实施医学观察。
Changzhou City, Jiangsu Province, recently issued the Notice on Emergency Diffusion in Search of Relevant Contacts: When Changzhou City cleared up confirmed cases of coronavirus infection, it found the 27th confirmed case of coronavirus infection.
对此，海底捞方面相关负责人告诉界面新闻，常州新北区丰臣国际店是该顾客众多行为轨迹中的一部分，门店接到相关部门通知后积极配合防疫检查，并对店面进行全面消毒；门店积极配合防疫机构进行顾客信息收集、反馈，并配合联络官方划定的接触者，同时密切关注曾服务过顾客的员工，目前身体状况正常。
In this regard, the relevant officials told the interface news, Changzhou New North District Fengchen International Shop is a part of the customer's numerous activities, the store received notification from the relevant departments actively cooperate with the epidemic prevention agencies to collect customer information, feedback, and contact the official contact, and closely monitored the customer service staff, the current state of health is normal.
海底捞防疫工作简报显示，海底捞公司于1月23日成立防控小组，搭建第三方专家顾问团队优化防控。
The briefing showed that the company set up a prevention and control team on January 23 to set up a team of third-party experts to optimize control.
界面新闻得知，海底捞集团的防疫总指挥部由董事长张勇担任总指挥，分别从组织架构搭建、门店员工安置与防疫、紧急上报机制、物资供应分配、资金调度管理等方面分工负责。
Interface News learned that the General Command of Sanitary Surveillance of the Submarine Fishing Group is under the overall command of Chairman Zhang Yong, who is responsible for organizational structure, store staff placement and epidemic prevention, emergency reporting mechanism, distribution of supplies, and fund management.
1月23日，海底捞成立武汉门店防疫现场指挥部，由武汉五店店经理担任现场总指挥，主责武汉地区27家门店疫情应对工作和员工安置。
On January 23, Wuhan Ganyuan epidemic prevention field command was set up, with Wuhan Wudian store manager as the overall command, mainly responsible for the response to the epidemic situation in Wuhan 27 stores and staff resettlement.
另外，海底捞总指挥部搭建16人的心理辅导团队，对员工进行心理疏导。
In addition, the General Command of bottom fishing set up a 16-person psychological counselling team, psychological counseling staff.
今日，海底捞防疫总指挥部向武汉金银潭医院和武汉大学人民医院定向捐赠4万盒自煮火锅。
Today, the General Command for Disease Control and Prevention donated 40,000 boxes of self-heating pot to Wuhan Gold and Silver Pool Hospital and Wuhan University People's Hospital.
2月12日起，海底捞将通过湖北省慈善总会，每天捐赠2万盒自煮火锅给湖北的医护人员，直到湖北疫情平稳。
From February 12, the bottom fishing will donate 20,000 boxes of self-heating pot to Hubei medical personnel every day through the Hubei Charity Association until the outbreak is stable.
此前，界面新闻曾报道过，2月2日，海底捞发布公告称，考虑到近期疫情发展情况，中国内地门店停业时间将会继续延长。
Earlier, the Interface News reported that on February 2, the bottom fishing announced that, in view of the recent outbreak of the disease, the closure of stores in mainland China will continue to be extended.
该公司此前决定于1月26日至1月31日暂停中国内地门店的营业。
The company had previously decided to suspend business at its mainland stores from January 26 to January 31.
公司外送服务也已暂停。
Corporate outsourcing services have also been suspended.
